name: ALL-IN (NFT Community)
description:
The backstory of this piece came from joining a Twitter Space. The Space started as a way to try and sell your art. What I found was "COMMUNITY". I manged to hear some amazing stories and ended up following some new wonderful and talented artists. This inspired me to create this piece and the vision is of a sports team where all the players come in to form a huddle and they end up breaking it down as they are "ALL-IN"

ScD-ArtWorks
